name: Right Click Disable
description: The Right-Click, Save As argument is a stance of people who do not believe in the value of internet art (specifically crypto art). The meme is often used in a satirical nature by those who want to ridicule people who claim that NFTs are worthless because it is possible to download the image. Right-Click, Save As is a running joke among most people in the crypto art community with many finding the argument holds no value.
